     <div type="author_to_the_reader">
   <pb facs="1"/>
   <head>The Author to the Reader.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>If Sathans might and force of sinne</l>
      <l>Heere seemes thy soule to wound,</l>
      <l>A soueraigne salue this booke prescribes,</l>
      <l>Direct to cure it sound.</l>
   </lg>
   <lg>
      <l>Esteeme this salue, and exercise</l>
      <l>Each day and night the same,</l>
      <l>So shall your soule well cured be</l>
      <l>Which sinne brought out of frame:</l>
   </lg>
   <lg>
      <l>Regard it more then worldly wealth,</l>
      <l>No treasure like to this,</l>
      <l>No mony can buy saue to cure▪</l>
      <l>Our soule, if this should misse.</l>
   </lg>
   <closer>
      <signed>I. A. Minister and Preacher of Gods Word.</signed>
   </closer>
</div>
